<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.9">
<l>tēṉōṭu vaṇṭālun tirumā liruñcōlai</l>
<l>tāṉiṭamāk koṇṭāṉ taṭamalark kaṇṇikkāy</l>
<l>āṉviṭaiyē ḻaṉṟaṭarttāṟ kāḷāṉā rallātār</l>
<l>māṉiṭava rallareṉ ṟeṉmaṉattē vaittēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have fixed in my mind that those who have not become servants</l>
<l>To the one who once conquered seven bulls</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of the one with wide bud eyes,</l>
<l>The one who took as his place Tirumāliruñcōlai, where hum bees with honey,</l>
<l rend="indent">Are not [even] human.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
